Martin John Christopher Freeman (born 8 September 1971) is an English actor who portrayed Arthur Dent in the 2005 film adaption of The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy. 

He is best known for his roles as Tim Canterbury in The Office, Dr. Watson in Sherlock, and Bilbo Baggins in Peter Jackson's three-part adaptation of The Hobbit. Film 
